Varde Plans Debt Swap to Keep Control in Crest, Telegraph Says

-- B y   Z i j i n g   W u
-- 
2011-05-01T08:57:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-01/varde-plans-debt-swap-to-keep-control-in-crest-telegraph-says.html
Varde Partners LLP, a U.S. hedge fund,
plans to convert 359 million pounds ($600 million) of debt into
equity as part of its plan to secure ownership in Crest
Nicholson Plc, according to the Sunday Telegraph.  New accounts at  Companies House  say the swap will allow
Crest, the U.K. housebuilder, to extend bank facilities till
2015, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zijing Wu in London at 
